<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body class="bg-white">
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
    
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="text-gray-600 body-font">
      <div class="container mx-auto flex px-5 py-24 md:flex-row flex-col items-center">
        <div class="lg:flex-grow md:w-1/2 lg:pr-24 md:pr-16 flex flex-col md:items-start md:text-left mb-16 md:mb-0 items-center text-center">
          <h1 class="title-font sm:text-4xl text-3xl mb-4 font-medium text-gray-900">Building Resilience, Fostering Peace</h1>
          <p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed">Peace and Humanitarian Initiative Trust is dedicated to promoting sustainable peace, advancing human rights, and delivering life-saving humanitarian aid to vulnerable communities across the globe.</p>
          <div class="flex justify-center">
            <a href="/strategy.html" class="inline-flex text-white bg-blue-500 border-0 py-2 px-6 focus:outline-none hover:bg-blue-600 rounded text-lg">See Our Strategy</a>
            <a href="/donate" class="ml-4 inline-flex text-gray-700 bg-gray-100 border-0 py-2 px-6 focus:outline-none hover:bg-gray-200 rounded text-lg">Donate</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:max-w-lg lg:w-full md:w-1/2 w-5/6">
          <img class="object-contain w-full h-auto max-h-96" alt="Peace Dove - Symbol of Hope and Harmony" src="/public/peace-dove-hero.png" style="background: transparent;">
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Addressing Critical Challenges Section -->
    <section class="text-gray-600 body-font bg-gray-50">
      <div class="container px-5 py-24 mx-auto">
        <div class="flex flex-col text-center w-full mb-20">
          <h2 class="text-xs text-blue-500 tracking-widest font-medium title-font mb-1">CRITICAL CHALLENGES</h2>
          <h1 class="sm:text-3xl text-2xl font-medium title-font mb-4 text-gray-900">Addressing Critical Challenges</h1>
          <p class="lg:w-2/3 mx-auto leading-relaxed text-base">In regions affected by conflict, climate change, and poverty, communities face systemic challenges. We are on the ground with a plan to provide critical support.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap -m-4 text-center">
          <div class="p-4 md:w-1/4 sm:w-1/2 w-full">
            <div class="border-2 border-gray-200 px-4 py-6 rounded-lg">
              <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" class="text-blue-500 w-12 h-12 mb-3 inline-block" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H5a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"></path>
                <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle>
                <path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 00-3-3.87m-4-12a4 4 0 010 7.75"></path>
              </svg>
              <h2 class="title-font font-medium text-lg text-gray-900">Conflict & Displacement</h2>
              <p class="leading-relaxed">Facilitating dialogue and community-driven peacebuilding to reduce violence and create lasting stability.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 md:w-1/4 sm:w-1/2 w-full">
            <div class="border-2 border-gray-200 px-4 py-6 rounded-lg">
              <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" class="text-blue-500 w-12 h-12 mb-3 inline-block" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M3 18v-6a9 9 0 0118 0v6"></path>
                <path d="M21 19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1a2 2 0 01-2-2v-3a2 2 0 012-2h3zM3 19a2 2 0 002 2h1a2 2 0 002-2v-3a2 2 0 00-2-2H3z"></path>
              </svg>
              <h2 class="title-font font-medium text-lg text-gray-900">Climate Disasters</h2>
              <p class="leading-relaxed">Helping communities prepare for and respond to floods, droughts, and other climate-related emergencies.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 md:w-1/4 sm:w-1/2 w-full">
            <div class="border-2 border-gray-200 px-4 py-6 rounded-lg">
              <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" class="text-blue-500 w-12 h-12 mb-3 inline-block" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"></path>
              </svg>
              <h2 class="title-font font-medium text-lg text-gray-900">Poverty & Inequality</h2>
              <p class="leading-relaxed">Empowering individuals with vocational training, resources, and opportunities to build self-reliant futures.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 md:w-1/4 sm:w-1/2 w-full">
            <div class="border-2 border-gray-200 px-4 py-6 rounded-lg">
              <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" class="text-blue-500 w-12 h-12 mb-3 inline-block" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M22 12h-4l-3 9L9 3l-3 9H2"></path>
              </svg>
              <h2 class="title-font font-medium text-lg text-gray-900">Limited Access to Basic Services</h2>
              <p class="leading-relaxed">Improving access to clean water, food security, and healthcare for crisis-affected populations.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Our Framework for Action Section -->
    <section class="text-gray-600 body-font">
      <div class="container px-5 py-24 mx-auto">
        <div class="flex flex-col text-center w-full mb-20">
          <h2 class="text-xs text-blue-500 tracking-widest font-medium title-font mb-1">OUR FRAMEWORK</h2>
          <h1 class="sm:text-3xl text-2xl font-medium title-font mb-4 text-gray-900">Our Framework for Action</h1>
          <p class="lg:w-2/3 mx-auto leading-relaxed text-base">Our work is built on four key pillars that ensure a comprehensive and sustainable impact in the communities we serve.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap">
          <div class="xl:w-1/4 lg:w-1/2 md:w-full px-8 py-6 border-l-2 border-gray-200 border-opacity-60">
            <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-900 font-medium title-font mb-2">Humanitarian Relief</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed text-base mb-4">Providing immediate, life-saving assistance—food, shelter, and medical care—to communities impacted by natural disasters, displacement, or war.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="xl:w-1/4 lg:w-1/2 md:w-full px-8 py-6 border-l-2 border-gray-200 border-opacity-60">
            <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-900 font-medium title-font mb-2">Conflict Resolution & Peacebuilding</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed text-base mb-4">Fostering dialogue, mediation, and reconciliation to reduce violence and build sustainable peace in conflict-affected communities.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="xl:w-1/4 lg:w-1/2 md:w-full px-8 py-6 border-l-2 border-gray-200 border-opacity-60">
            <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-900 font-medium title-font mb-2">Community Empowerment</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed text-base mb-4">Supporting local development through education, vocational training, micro-finance, and capacity-building programs.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="xl:w-1/4 lg:w-1/2 md:w-full px-8 py-6 border-l-2 border-gray-200 border-opacity-60">
            <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-900 font-medium title-font mb-2">Human Rights Advocacy</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed text-base mb-4">Championing civil liberties, gender equality, and the protection of marginalized groups through policy engagement and grassroots mobilization.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Our Strategic Initiatives Section -->
    <section id="strategic-initiatives" class="text-gray-600 body-font bg-gray-50">
      <div class="container px-5 py-24 mx-auto">
        <div class="flex flex-col text-center w-full mb-20">
          <h2 class="text-xs text-blue-500 tracking-widest font-medium title-font mb-1">STRATEGIC INITIATIVES</h2>
          <h1 class="sm:text-3xl text-2xl font-medium title-font mb-4 text-gray-900">Our Strategic Initiatives</h1>
          <p class="lg:w-2/3 mx-auto leading-relaxed text-base">We have developed targeted, community-focused programs to address urgent needs. These initiatives form our roadmap for creating sustainable change in Zimbabwe's most vulnerable districts and are ready for implementation with the support of our partners.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap -m-4">
          <div class="xl:w-1/3 md:w-1/2 p-4">
            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
              <img class="h-40 rounded w-full object-cover object-center mb-6" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1589182373726-e4f658ab50b0?w=500" alt="Dry landscape">
              <h3 class="tracking-widest text-blue-500 text-xs font-medium title-font">TSHOLOTSHO DISTRICT</h3>
              <h2 class="text-lg text-gray-900 font-medium title-font mb-4">Drought and Flood Resilience</h2>
              <p class="leading-relaxed text-base">This program will reduce community vulnerability through climate-smart agriculture, improved water access, and the establishment of local disaster committees and early warning systems.</p>
              <a href="/initiatives.html" class="text-blue-500 inline-flex items-center mt-3">Learn About the Plan
                <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" class="w-4 h-4 ml-2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
                </svg>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="xl:w-1/3 md:w-1/2 p-4">
            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
              <img class="h-40 rounded w-full object-cover object-center mb-6" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1547683905-f686c993aae5?w=500" alt="Community meeting">
              <h3 class="tracking-widest text-blue-500 text-xs font-medium title-font">CHIPINGE & CHIMANIMANI</h3>
              <h2 class="text-lg text-gray-900 font-medium title-font mb-4">Cyclone Preparedness</h2>
              <p class="leading-relaxed text-base">Following the devastation of Cyclone Idai, this initiative is designed to strengthen community-based preparedness by developing disaster management plans, installing early warning systems, and restoring ecosystems.</p>
              <a href="/initiatives.html" class="text-blue-500 inline-flex items-center mt-3">Learn About the Plan
                <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" class="w-4 h-4 ml-2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
                </svg>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="xl:w-1/3 md:w-1/2 p-4">
            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
              <img class="h-40 rounded w-full object-cover object-center mb-6" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1625246333195-78d9c38ad449?w=500" alt="Solar water pump">
              <h3 class="tracking-widest text-blue-500 text-xs font-medium title-font">BEITBRIDGE DISTRICT</h3>
              <h2 class="text-lg text-gray-900 font-medium title-font mb-4">Drought Mitigation and Empowerment</h2>
              <p class="leading-relaxed text-base">Our goal for Beitbridge is to address chronic food insecurity by constructing solar-powered boreholes, providing drought-resistant seeds, and delivering vocational training to over 5,000 households.</p>
              <a href="/initiatives.html" class="text-blue-500 inline-flex items-center mt-3">Learn About the Plan
                <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" class="w-4 h-4 ml-2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
                </svg>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- About PHI Snippet Section -->
    <section class="text-gray-600 body-font">
      <div class="container px-5 py-24 mx-auto">
        <div class="flex flex-col text-center w-full mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-xs text-blue-500 tracking-widest font-medium title-font mb-1">ABOUT PHI</h2>
          <h1 class="sm:text-3xl text-2xl font-medium title-font mb-4 text-gray-900">A Foundation of Trust and Commitment</h1>
          <p class="lg:w-2/3 mx-auto leading-relaxed text-base">Peace and Humanitarian Initiative Trust (PHI) is a registered non-governmental organization (MA0000063/2019, Protocol 04/19) founded by BASTER WILLIE MAGWIZI and TIMOTHY SITHOLE. We are committed to transparency, accountability, and a community-centered model that prioritizes local voices and sustainable impact.</p>
          <button onclick="window.location.href='/about'" class="flex mx-auto mt-6 text-white bg-blue-500 border-0 py-2 px-8 focus:outline-none hover:bg-blue-600 rounded text-lg">Meet Our Team</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Final Call to Action Section -->
    <section class="text-gray-600 body-font bg-blue-500">
      <div class="container px-5 py-24 mx-auto text-center">
        <div class="flex flex-col w-full">
          <h1 class="sm:text-3xl text-2xl font-medium title-font mb-4 text-white">Partner With Us to Build a Better Future</h1>
          <p class="lg:w-2/3 mx-auto leading-relaxed text-base text-white mb-8">Your support will help launch these vital initiatives, bringing tangible hope and resilience to communities in need. Join us in turning strategic plans into life-changing action.</p>
          <div class="flex justify-center">
            <a href="/donate" class="inline-flex text-blue-600 bg-white border-0 py-2 px-8 focus:outline-none hover:bg-gray-100 rounded text-lg">Donate Now</a>
            <a href="/contact" class="ml-4 inline-flex text-white bg-transparent border border-white py-2 px-8 focus:outline-none hover:bg-blue-600 rounded text-lg">Become a Partner</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
